# {{APP_NAME}}

A personal web application built with Go + HTMX.

## Development

```bash
# Run locally
go run main.go

# Access at http://localhost:{{APP_PORT}}
```

## Configuration

Edit `config.yaml` to add users:

```yaml
users:
  - username: yourname
    password_hash: $2a$10$...  # Generate with ../../scripts/hash-password.sh
```

## Building

```bash
# Build binary
go build -o {{APP_NAME}} .

# Run
./{{APP_NAME}}
```

## Docker

```bash
# Build image
docker build -t {{APP_NAME}} .

# Run container
docker run -p {{APP_PORT}}:{{APP_PORT}} -v $(pwd)/data:/root/data {{APP_NAME}}
```
